Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:20.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know this ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:29.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The wound on my stomach is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:31.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Everything considered, it must've been her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:33.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia's healing power, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.78,0:00:49.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at any rate, seems I got out of \Nusing Return by Death this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:54.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But normally, wouldn't you wake up to a girl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:58.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,by your bed asking, "Are you awake," \Nafter she'd cared for you all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:01.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,For a story about being summoned to \Nanother world, it's kinda flawed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:12.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A looping hallway...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:15.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,One of those things where I can't \Nleave until I find the right room?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.66,0:01:19.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The typical pattern says that the \Nfirst door is likely to be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:24.98,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,What a profoundly aggravating \Nman you are, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.21,0:01:26.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,First NPC found!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:30.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,With that cold attitude, you're gonna \Nruin your cute face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:32.07,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, smile... Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:35.81,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,A derisive sneer is the only smile worth giving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:39.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mad because I guessed \Ncorrectly on the first try?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:41.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been a pretty lucky guesser...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:46.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand why game masters would \Nwant me in all the events, but sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:49.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So, what is this place, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:54.01,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, it's Betty's multi-purpose room, \Nboth library and bedroom, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:55.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about your token response.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:58.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you one of the manual girls everyone's into now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:00.86,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Betty's had just about enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:03.06,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Time to teach you a lesson, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:05.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:07.14,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:10.14,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Anything you'd like to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.14,0:02:11.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:24.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to me, you drill loli?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:28.24,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,I only collected the mana from your body, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:30.93,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,It confirmed that you are not an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:33.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're not human, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:36.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't mean your personality...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:38.74,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,It took you long enough to notice, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:41.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I take it back... Your personality isn't human, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:47.34,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Do not measure a proud, noble being \Nby your standards, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:26.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I know that ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:29.32,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he has awakened, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:31.16,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, he has awakened, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:34.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I, a denizen of the night, waking in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:36.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting all emotional...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:38.16,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better go to sleep a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:42.64,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,No, I woke up earlier, so this'll be the third.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.81,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a deadbeat thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that, Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:49.00,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, truly a loser's words. I heard him, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:49.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:52.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these two voices that \Nkeep criticizing me in stereo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:58.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Maid costumes exist in this world, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:02.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In my mind, maids were always the \Nvery personification of elegance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:05.07,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't so bad, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:10.65,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,How terrible. You are being violated \Nin our guest's mind, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:15.21,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,It is terrible. You are experiencing the ultimate \Nshame in our guest's mind, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:17.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate my capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:20.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're both fair prey in my fantasies...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:26.43,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you wake up more peacefully, Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:34.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever picked that outfit totally gets it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:36.85,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:39.31,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,but the fact that I know it's something \Nstupid is disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:41.55,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to this, Miss Emilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:44.48,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,My dear sister was just violated by that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:45.95,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen to this, Miss Emilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:48.58,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Rem was held prisoner and shamed by that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:50.98,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,And you two, don't tease him too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:53.60,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss Emilia. My sister is very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:55.75,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss Emilia. Rem is sorry, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:58.92,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, are you feeling all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.38,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Does anything feel off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:04.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, I'm just a little groggy from oversleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:06.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me, didn't you, Emilia-tan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:07.47,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? "Tan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.18,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,What does "tan" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.76,Default,Suburu,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, you can just ignore that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:14.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, though, thanks. You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.55,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm the one who should thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:22.15,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You barely know me, but you \Nrisked your life to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.44,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural I would heal your wounds afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:29.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then, once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's time to start a new day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:36.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This place really is huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:39.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The yard isn't so much a yard as a field.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:43.63,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Those are unusual movements. \NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:47.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,My homeland's ancient practice \Nof warm-up exercises.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:49.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Emilia-tan! Join me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Radio calisthenics, number 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Bounce on both feet to loosen up your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.97,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're kidding! What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just do what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:02.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drill the essence of radio calisthenics into you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:10.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Now, raise both arms and shout, "Victory!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.94,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,V-Victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:14.16,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Victory! Victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.00,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.41,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Subaru! Great morning, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:23.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since the wee hours of the morning, \Nit's been nothing but chaos for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:26.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Looping hallways and a mean \Nlittle girl on a rampage...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:30.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And then, shedding the sweat \Nof passion with Emilia-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:33.02,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make it sound so scandalous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:34.35,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Puck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I put you through so much yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:40.92,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Lia. I almost lost you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:43.67,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I can never thank Subaru enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:44.94,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I must do something for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:46.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:49.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let me pet your fur whenever I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:51.50,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:54.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,For a first-rate fur master such as myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:57.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,being able to love on the object of \Nyour petting affections anytime
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:08:01.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,is worth as much as a multimillionaire's riches!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, these ears...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:06.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with how soft you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.97,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Since I can kind of read your mind, \NI know you feel that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:10.76,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm amazed you can say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.27,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Lia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:16.72,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find any malice, hostility, or ill-intent in Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:19.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute how you call her "Lia," too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:22.20,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Not as cute as your "Emilia-tan"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.56,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You really are strange, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:33.99,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What brings you two here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:35.79,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Emilia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:39.58,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Our lord, Master Roswaal, has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.25,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Please come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:47.63,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching you from upstairs, \Nand you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.74,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem you are quite dumb, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:53.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you get off saying that, you loli?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:55.00,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,What does that word mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:58.03,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,I have never heard it before, and it irritates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.91,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Betty. Haven't seen you in four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.93,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been doing well and staying ladylike?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:04.39,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Bubby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:07.47,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:09.61,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Will you stay with me today, do you suppose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:10.82,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:13.49,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Let's finally relax together today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:15.93,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:18.34,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Bewildered, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:20.56,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Beatrice is so taken with Puck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:22.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Who even says "bewildered" nowadays?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:27.21,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,My, my! How unusual to see you here, Beatrice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:33.00,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy you've decided to dine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:36.58,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,That boy is more than enough of an \Naddle-brained fool for me, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:39.30,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Betty was only waiting for Bubby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:43.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You guys hired a clown to entertain \Nyou before each meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never understand how rich folks think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:47.72,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Subaru, that man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:51.48,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... It's quite all right, Miss Emilia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:52.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:58.85,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Only that I am the lord of this \Nmanor, Roswaal L. Mathers,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:00.45,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki Subaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:10.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is way better than normal food!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:14.42,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Despite her appearance, Rem's cooking \Nis quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:19.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So this was cooked by the one with \Nblue hair... Um, Rem-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:20.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You made this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:22.63,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do the cooking in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:27.89,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,My sister is not very good at cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:31.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, twins who are good at different things!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:33.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is your sister good at cleaning, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.59,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:38.74,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,My sister excels at housework, \Nparticularly cleaning and laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:42.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So, Rem-rin, you're good at cooking, \Nbut bad at cleaning and laundry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:46.55,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,No, I am generally good at all household tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:49.41,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I am also better at cleaning \Nand laundry than my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:51.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Does your sister even have a purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:54.09,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,You are truly a strange young man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:57.81,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,You come to the mansion of Margrave Mathers, \Nin the kingdom of Lugunica,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:11:01.49,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,but you claim to understand nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:04.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is something bad happening in this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.85,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is not in an agreeable state.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:12.52,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Lugunica's king is currently not present.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:16.60,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's no need to be concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:21.02,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is already quite aware of the reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:22.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:26.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I expected a "Now that you know my secret, \NI can't let you leave here alive" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:31.75,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Around the same time that the king went into hiding, \Nan epidemic began spreading through the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:34.81,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,The king and his children are the last of his line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:38.09,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,A council of wise men currently manages the nation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:42.43,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,and they are now in the process \Nof selecting a new king!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:45.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm starting to get the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:48.97,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,On top of the king's absence, the royal selection \Nis causing confusion in the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then, suddenly, I appear from another world—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:52.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'm totally suspect here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:55.06,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:12:00.19,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,you made contact with Miss Emilia, \Nthus becoming connected to my household!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:04.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why would the lord of the \Nmansion call her "Miss Emilia"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:10.70,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural to address someone of \Nhigher status with all due respect...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:13.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, so Emilia-tan would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:17.04,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,My current status is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:20.84,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,a candidate to become the Kingdom \Nof Lugunica's forty-second ruler,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:23.59,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,with Margrave Roswaal's backing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:24.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:26.69,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't trying to keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's that insignia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:36.20,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,This qualifies one to be a candidate for king.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:42.10,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It's a touchstone for determining \Nif one is worthy of the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:46.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Emilia-tan, you lost an insignia that \Nqualifies you to rule the kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:48.60,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put it like that! I didn't lose it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.24,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It was stolen from me by a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:54.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And what if you lose that thing, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:56.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Will a government office issue you another?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:13:01.21,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! If you'd lost it, then there \Nwould be no doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:04.67,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,If it were thought that one who \Ncan't even protect a tiny insignia
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:08.55,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,can't be entrusted with the nation's \Nrule, that would be the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:12.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, I did a damn good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:15.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This totally raises my expectations for a reward...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:19.55,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right. You were my true savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:20.96,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,So ask for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:25.32,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,You may have any reward you request. \NMerely state your desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:29.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I have but one request.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:36.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hire me to work in this mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:40.84,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Achoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:44.30,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't quite right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:47.12,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't there anything else that fit you, Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:49.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oddly, some of the girls' stuff fit me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:53.02,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Our deepest apologies, sir. I mean, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:55.89,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You look quite ridiculous, sir. I mean, Barusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:59.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Nee-sama, you just turned my \Nname into a blinding curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:03.18,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, looking at Barusu's ridiculous \Nappearance, do you notice anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:06.95,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,His shoulders are shaped funny, his legs \Nare short, and his eyes are scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:10.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything about two of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:13.03,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot allow you to work here \Nin such shady-looking attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.58,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,People would question Lord Roswaal's dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:19.75,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Let us alter the jacket, at least. \NRem, if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:22.66,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I have to study for the royal selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:24.05,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck with your work, too, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:26.97,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, leave it to me, Emilia-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:30.64,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I shall take your measurements. Stand still \Nand keep your back straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:37.35,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Please refrain from strange noises. It's unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:39.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That was beyond my control...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:41.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is awkward for a guy in multiple ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:43.32,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,This is the VIP room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:44.77,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,This is the bathing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:46.15,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,This is the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:48.21,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the lavatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:51.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In a mansion like this, the restroom must be huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:55.36,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,You're so great, Bubby! Your fur is the best—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:58.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I won't tell a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The feel of that fur would make anyone—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:03.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let me finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:08.51,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,That was Miss Beatrice's Door Crossing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:12.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a spell that can connect any \Ndoor in the mansion to her room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:15.51,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Once Miss Beatrice has eliminated her presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:18.96,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,there is no way to find her without \Ntrying every door in the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She's in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:24.20,Default,Pack,0000,0000,0000,,That was impressive, Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:26.44,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,You picked the right door again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a flag-crusher who makes game masters cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:31.86,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what you're saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:34.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:35.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ros-chi's little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:39.14,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never want to be his sister, I suppose! Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:42.62,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Betty is the librarian who oversees the \NRoswaal mansion's forbidden library.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:46.03,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Roswaal is the greatest \Nmagic-user in the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:48.69,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,He has many books that must not be seen by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:51.90,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Beatrice is contracted to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:54.02,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,If you get it now, then go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:57.93,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,This concludes our tour of the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.48,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:03.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's no use saying this after it's over,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:07.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but shouldn't Emilia-tan be the one \Nwith me for the tour event?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:11.88,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,If you have no questions, let us \Nget to your actual job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:14.41,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You will help me with my work, Barusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:18.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This must be where my hidden \Nskill as a butler reveals itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:22.21,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,My work today is caring for the front yard \Nand garden, helping to prepare lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:25.28,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,polishing the silver, airing the futons, \Nlaundry, bathroom cleaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:26.75,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,and the mansion's monthly soot cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:31.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.29,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,This is Rem. Do you have a moment, Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:37.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'm good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:39.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do anything weird, so come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:42.16,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Your permission actually makes \Nyou sound less credible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:43.48,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You already finished it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:50.23,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,When it is Lord Roswaal's clothing, \Nmy priority is to take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.48,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,But since this is yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:53.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just imply that you cut corners?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:58.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit it, but it's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Do I look good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:02.53,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Combined with the rarity of gray clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:05.55,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,no one in any kind of strange \Ngarment could rival you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:07.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Not a compliment at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:09.00,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This one's easy. Got a needle and thread?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:15.09,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I brought them. Shall I repair it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:16.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:19.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate my sewing skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:24.43,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I am surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:27.31,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I must give you full marks for your sewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:32.65,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Like you, however, it does not seem very useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:34.07,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:38.32,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You may get full marks for sewing, but you \Nare still useless with a knife, Barusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:42.24,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,As always, you make such a lovely image \Nwhen peeling vegetables, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Your bias is so blatant, it's almost comforting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:47.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a comment on my work, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:50.29,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I pity the farmer who grew those vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:52.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You're breaking my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:55.27,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You do not know how to handle a knife, Barusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:57.72,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You should hold the knife still, turning the vegetable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:01.05,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly speaking, my best dish is steamed tatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:04.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that with such a triumphant look?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:08.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,My favorite blade, Shooting Star, \Nwill show you a thing or two—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It sliced right through me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:26.34,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,It's been five days since Subaru-kun \Ncame to the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:28.02,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,How has he been?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By now, we should be seeing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:33.38,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking, laundry, cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:35.30,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,He is useless at all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:37.20,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,How strict of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:37.67,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:40.39,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,What of his potential as a spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:45.53,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot deny it exists, but I believe \Nthe possibility is slim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:47.18,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,For better or worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Specifically for worse, he is too conspicuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.36,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,And if he's too conspicuous...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:57.24,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that possibility, he certainly is carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:02.49,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,As I personally see it, interfering would be wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:05.22,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,They are only children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we let them be, nothing will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:16.93,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't that fun to watch, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:20.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm with you, nothing is boring, Emilia-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:23.52,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me happy, even if \Nyou're only flattering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:30.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we haven't had a chance \Nto talk for the past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:34.69,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It must be difficult for \Nyou to learn your work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:37.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is! It's killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:40.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could be sequentially comforted in \Nyour arms, on your chest, and on your lap—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:44.41,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. If you can joke around \Nlike that, you must be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:51.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The moon sure is pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:54.63,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's far beyond our reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:58.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I got a really touching response, without even trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:02.84,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, don't you think you're \Na bit lacking in ambition?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:03.89,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Like that time with Puck,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:07.34,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,and in the capital, when you asked for my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:09.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't get it, Emilia-tan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:12.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want what I want at that exact moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I want it from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.07,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:21.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, I wanted to know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:26.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In a new land, nervous, and unsure of the future, \NI had no expectations for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:27.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about it calmly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:30.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,there were probably other things \NI should have wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:34.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't lie to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:40.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Same with the request I made to Ros-chi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:43.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm flat broke right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:45.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I could cheat him out of a fortune and live it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:49.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but I can just as easily obtain \Na source of livelihood, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:53.53,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, couldn't you have become a permanent \Nguest, rather than an employee?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:54.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:00.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, talk about pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:02.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You should keep your efforts a secret, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:05.53,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to use my healing magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm fine like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:08.07,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:12.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of hard to explain, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:15.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is proof of the effort I put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.88,0:21:18.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't actually dislike exerting myself, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:21.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Learning to do something I couldn't do before...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:23.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:29.07,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Yes, I think you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.13,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Subaru, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:33.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's with that reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:35.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is where you fall for me, all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.24,0:21:36.39,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I never initially fell for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:41.28,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you're so silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:44.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,EMA...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:46.18,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:48.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's short for "Emilia-tan, major angel."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:51.16,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thanking you, and you're joking around again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:55.07,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I know you're working hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:57.98,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,but how did your hands get so torn up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:22:00.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I cut this one with knives in the kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:03.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And this is from the evening when \NI went shopping in town,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:06.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and a little animal some kids \Nwere playing with bit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:08.95,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't the result of your effort?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:10.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids were ruthless,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:14.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,hitting and kicking me, and wiping their \Nrunny noses on me. It sucked, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:18.12,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You do seem like you'd be good \Nwith small children, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.12,0:22:22.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Wanna come with me \Ntomorrow, to get revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:25.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, to watch the kids and the small animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.03,0:22:28.74,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't that I don't want to go with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.04,0:22:30.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:34.05,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But if I'm with you, it might cause trouble for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.05,0:22:36.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:37.84,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.84,0:22:41.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I am! I hang on every word you say, Emilia-tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:44.00,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:48.73,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Only during a break from my studies and \Nwhen your work is done, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:53.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:02.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, loli girl! You're still up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.78,0:23:06.53,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,So now you can break through my Door \NCrossing like it's natural, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.00,0:23:09.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just wanted to say hello before going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.63,0:23:11.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Can I try that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.73,0:23:15.33,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Only Bubby may touch me, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.61,0:23:17.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No fair that only you can have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.82,0:23:19.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm in a good mood, so I can let it go—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.47,0:23:20.54,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! Just get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.02,0:23:28.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That has nothing to do with Betty, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:30.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,For our date tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.37,0:23:33.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to come up with an excuse \Nto ditch those kids at the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:37.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but first, I've gotta learn where all the good \Nviews and flower fields and stuff are...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:40.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I can't sleep while I'm thinking about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.79,0:23:42.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.35,0:23:47.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,One Puck... Two Pucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:51.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred and one Pucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.78,0:23:57.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A new dawn has come! A dawn of hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.92,0:24:01.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki Subaru will make giant strides today...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.67,0:24:04.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You were in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.49,0:24:05.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.84,0:24:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have said something!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:12.74,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, Sister... Our guest appears \Nto be a bit confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.74,0:24:16.54,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, Rem... It looks as though \Nour guest has gone crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.54,0:24:18.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you calling me a guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.34,0:24:21.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You two and your jokes...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.14,0:24:32.28,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The wounds
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.28,0:24:35.82,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The {\c&HB5714D&}Happy {\c&HFFFFFF&}Roswaal Mansion Family
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.71,0:24:33.75,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,are gone.
